# JobHub вЂ” Job Opportunity Hub

A full-featured job board web application built with Django 4.x, Bootstrap 5, and MySQL.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer      | Technology                                  |
|------------|---------------------------------------------|
| Frontend   | Bootstrap 5, HTML5, CSS3, DM Sans / Playfair Display |
| Backend    | Django 4.2 (Python 3.10+)                  |
| Database   | MySQL 8.x                                   |
| Forms      | django-crispy-forms + crispy-bootstrap5     |
| Auth       | Django built-in + custom AbstractUser       |
| File storage | Local (Pillow for images, PDF for resumes) |

---

## Features

- **Role-based auth** вЂ” Job Seeker & Employer roles with separate registration flows
- **Job listings** вЂ” Post, edit, delete, feature jobs with categories & filters
- **Applications** вЂ” Apply with cover letter + PDF resume upload; track status
- **Dashboards** вЂ” Separate employer & jobseeker dashboards with stats
- **Subscriptions** вЂ” Free / Pro / Elite (jobseeker) and Starter / Growth / Enterprise (employer) plans
- **Search & filter** вЂ” Keyword, location, job type, category
- **Admin panel** вЂ” Django admin for full moderation

